snippet.title: The WORST Like to Dislike Ratio On YOUTUBE
snippet.description:
A video from Access Hollywood called Amber Heard's 2020 Takeaway: 'Adapt & Survive' has gotten the worst like to dislike ration in the history of youtube with a 1% like ratio. This is all because Amber Heard, Amber very publicly called Johnny out for being alcoholic & abusive. The alcoholic part might very well be true, but the evidence towards abusive - especially physically - was lacking. Awhile later, after Depp's career had been annihilated by these accusations, video evidence of Amber being physically & emotionally abusive towards her then-husband was leaked.




Twitter - Kuda The Menace - https://twitter.com/KudaMenace?lang=en 


Discord - Kuda World - https://discord.gg/VpFNvSK 




Subscriber Goal 2,894/10,000
